{"id":"perf-250","category":"rum","difficulty":"expert","title":"Building a performance culture","performance_problem":{"symptom":"Performance regresses over time without discipline","metric_impact":"--","business_impact":"Slow degradation"},"diagnosis_steps":["No budgets","No alerting","No retros"],"anti_patterns_to_avoid":["Performance as someone else's problem","No SLOs","Only react to incidents"],"reasoning":"Senior thinking:\n1. Performance budgets per route + CI gate.\n2. RUM dashboards visible to all.\n3. Quarterly performance reviews.\n4. Each PR considers perf impact.\n5. Performance owner per area.","solution":"// docs/PERFORMANCE_CULTURE.md\n/*\n## Performance principles\n1. Measure first, optimize second\n2. Budgets per route enforced in CI\n3. RUM data shapes decisions\n4. Profile before claiming a fix\n5. Performance considered in design reviews\n6. Quarterly perf retros surface trends\n\n## Tools\n- Lighthouse CI for synthetic\n- web-vitals + custom RUM for real users\n- React Profiler for component-level\n- pg_stat_statements for DB\n- clinic.js for Node\n*/","before_metrics":"--","after_metrics":"Sustained perf","trade_offs":"Process discipline","regression_prevention":"This IS the culture","what_breaks_naive_approach":"Without culture: bit rot."}
